      "date": "2024-03-12 11:33:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nDo you know when this happen? What is the state of the connection?\nThe OFED source code seems to send this event when handling a REP request, so this should part of the connection process.\nMaybe this is a race between 2 connection errors.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
