        "username": "ssmirnov"
      },
      "date": "2024-03-12 15:02:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nFrom the customer description (see linked ticket) it looks like servers got reconfigured to add a new lnet, then MDT got started fine, but later starting OST caused MDT to crash",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
